Package: solar4r
Title: Machine Learning Tools for Solar Power Imputation and Forecasting
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Kostas", "Passadis", , "kpassadis@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A specialized toolkit for national-grid scale solar power forecasting. 
    Includes physically-informed feature engineering using optimized beta-weights 
    to account for hardware geometry, solar geometry calculations, and 
    Support Vector Machine (SVM) regression for curtailment imputation.
